y<\/li>\n<li>Twitter: 8:00 am Monday and Thursday<\/li>\n<li>LinkedIn 9:00 am Tuesday and Wednesday<\/li>\n<li>TikTok: 7:00 pm Thursday<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><strong>Sprout Social<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/sproutsocial.com\/insights\/best-times-to-post-on-social-media\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sprout Social analyzed<\/a> social media use from over 30,000 customers to check when is the best time to post on social media.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>Overall<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Best time overall: 9 am to 10 am Tuesday through Thursday<\/li>\n<li>Best days: Tuesday through Thursday<\/li>\n<li>Worst day to post: Sunday<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><strong>Facebook<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Sprout Social measured in US central time, but keep in mind that <a href=\"https:\/\/umbrellaxact.com\/service\/facebook-advertising-with-guaranteed-results\/\">Facebook<\/a> has a global audience. That means that when its 3 am CST in Chicago, it\u2019s 2 pm in Delhi India, for example.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Best times:\n<ul>\n<li>3 am Monday through Friday<\/li>\n<li>10 am and noon Tuesday<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Best days: Tuesday through Friday<\/li>\n<li>Worst day to post: Saturday<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><strong>Instagram<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Best time\n<ul>\n<li>11 am Monday<\/li>\n<li>10 am to 1 pm Tuesday and Wednesday<\/li>\n<li>10 am to 11 am Thursday and Friday<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Best days: Tuesday and Wednesday<\/li>\n<li>Worst day to post: Sunday<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><strong>Twitter<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Best time: Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Friday and Saturday at 9 am<\/li>\n<li>Best days: Tuesday and Wednesday<\/li>\n<li>Worst day to post: Sunday<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><strong>LinkedIn<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Best time: Tuesday 10 am to noon<\/li>\n<li>Best days: Wednesday and Thursday<\/li>\n<li>Worst day to post: Saturday and Sunday<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><strong>TikTok<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Best time\n<ul>\n<li>2 pm to 3 pm Tuesday<\/li>\n<li>1 pm to 3 pm Wednesday and Thursday<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Best days: Wednesday and Thursday<\/li>\n<li>Worst day to post: Sunday<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><strong>Hubspot<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/blog.hubspot.com\/marketing\/best-times-post-pin-tweet-social-media-infographic\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hubspot derived<\/a> its best times to post on social media by surveying over 300 marketers rather than directly analyzing thousands of social media posts.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>Facebook<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Best times\n<ul>\n<li>6 pm to 9 pm (26% of marketers)<\/li>\n<li>3 pm to 6 pm (23% of marketers)<\/li>\n<li>9 pm to 12 pm (21% of marketers)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Best times for agriculture, food and beverage, travel and hospitality: 9 am to 12 pm<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Best day: Saturday<\/li>\n<li>Worst day: Monday<\/li>\n<li>Worst times\n<ul>\n<li>6 a.m. to 9 am<\/li>\n<li>9 pm to 12 am<\/li>\n<li>12 pm to 3 pm<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><strong>Instagram<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Best times\n<ul>\n<li>6 pm to 9 pm (24% of marketers)<\/li>\n<li>3 pm to 6 pm (20% of marketers)<\/li>\n<li>9 ma and 12 pm (20% of marketers)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Best day:\n<ul>\n<li>Saturday for B2C brands<\/li>\n<li>Friday for B2B brands<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Worst day: Monday<\/li>\n<li>Worst times\n<ul>\n<li>6 am to 9 am<\/li>\n<li>9 pm to 12 am<\/li>\n<li>12 pm to 3 pm (except for manufacturing and materials businesses who report much success in that time frame)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><strong>Twitter<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Best times\n<ul>\n<li>noon to 9 pm (27% of marketers)<\/li>\n<li>3 pm to 6 pm (24% of marketers)<\/li>\n<li>12 to 3 pm (17% of marketers)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Best day: Friday<\/li>\n<li>Worst time: 6 am to 12 pm<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><strong>LinkedIn<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Best times\n<ul>\n<li>6 pm to 9 pm (26% of marketers)<\/li>\n<li>3 pm to 6 pm (23% of marketers)<\/li>\n<li>12 p